<h2 class="wlentry" id="e20121130-tg_news"><a href="permalinks/news_e20121130-tg.htm#e20121130-tg_news">mksh R41 released</a></h2>
<div class="wlsubtitle">30.11.2012 by <a href="mailto:tg@mirbsd.org">tg@</a></div>
<div class="wltagtitle">Tags: <a href="tag_mksh_all.htm#e20121130-tg_news">mksh</a></div>
</div>
<p>The <a href="mksh.htm">MirBSD Korn Shell R41</a> has finally
 been released. This is a major “everything” version with important fixes
 as well as new features and behavioural changes. Sorry for the delay.</p>
<p>See also the:</p><ul>
 <li><a href="mksh.htm#r41">detailed changelog</a></li>
 <li><a href="mksh.htm#p41">packagers’ info</a></li>
 <li><a href="mksh.htm#c41">users’ caveats</a></li>
 <li><a href="/MirOS/cats/mir/mksh/mksh-R41.cat1.gz">Preformatted
  manual page</a> (<a href="/MirOS/cats/mir/mksh/mksh-R41.htm.gz">HTML</a>,
  <a href="/MirOS/cats/mir/mksh/mksh-R41.pdf">PDF</a>, <a
  href="/MirOS/cats/mir/mksh/mksh-R41.txt.gz">plaintext</a>)</li>
 <li><a href="/MirOS/dist/mir/mksh/mksh-R41.tgz">Download</a>
  <strong>NEW</strong> as <a href="htman/i386/man1/gzip.htm" class="manlink">gzip(1)</a>’d us<!-- --><a href="htman/i386/man1/tar.htm" class="manlink">tar(1)</a> distfile!</li>
 <li>OpenSuSE Buildservice <a
  href="http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/shells/CentOS_5/src/mksh-41-1.1.src.rpm">SRPM</a>
  (and more, including binaries; just browse that directory tree)</li>
 <li><a href="http://news.gmane.org/gmane.os.miros.mksh">mailing list</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
